OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FClear skies
OL,6,Fto end the day for most. Overnight,
OL,7,Flow cloud moves in from the sea to
OL,8,Faffect many places by the morning. The
OL,9,Fwind eases slightly for many places
OL,10,Finland, but remains breezy along the
OL,11,Fcoast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FMorning cloud gradually
OL,14,Fbreaking up to give sunny spells by
OL,15,Fthe afternoon. Above average
OL,16,Ftemperatures inland, around normal
OL,17,Falong the coast, but the breeze taking
OL,18,Fthe edge off the heat.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
